snippet.textDisplay: Whats CRAZY? Im two toned too but I do the same powder over primer thing you usually do EXCEPT WHEN I COLOR CORRECT I USE EYESHADOW and then go over it with foundation after. I cant layer too many liquid or cream or whatever you would call foundation and concealer. So when i powder over my primer i color correct with a peachy eyeshadow and it keeps me matte.
